# Paywaz API Spec (Placeholder)

This file holds early planning notes for the public API schema. Production-ready endpoints will be documented in `openapi/openapi.yaml` once available.

## Authentication (preview)
- JWT-based access
- Non-custodial wallet support
- Merchant API Keys (coming soon)

For more details, see `docs/authentication.md`.

## Example request (preview)
```json
{
  "amount": "49.99",
  "currency": "PZUSD",
  "merchant_id": "your-merchant-id",
  "metadata": {
    "orderId": "12345"
  }
}
```
